title.narrative: USAID Monitoring and Evaluation Support Activity (MEASURE II)

description.narrative: (Bosnia and Herzegovina): USAID's monitoring, evaluation, and learning (MEL) support project, MEASURE II, will provide the mission with technical, analytics, advisory, training, monitoring, evaluating, and learning services. The project will conduct a wide range of flexible, demand-driven services. These services will include performance and impact evaluations, assessments, national surveys and similar polls, and support for the mission's Performance Management Plan and project MEL plans.This project is the mission's essential implementing mechanism for meeting the administration policy priority of "Ensuring Effectiveness and Accountability to the U.S. Taxpayer" as contained in the Joint Strategic Plan and the EUR Joint Regional Strategy.
